results.name: Ordinal transform of A081373; Ordinal transform of the {ordinal transform of A000010}.
link: Antti Karttunen, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..65537
maple: b:= proc() 0 end: g:= proc() 0 end:
h:= proc(n) option remember; local t;
a:= proc(n) option remember; local t;
program: ordinal_transform(invec) = { my(om = Map(), outvec = vector(length(invec)), pt); for(i=1, length(invec), if(mapisdefined(om,invec[i]), pt = mapget(om, invec[i]), pt = 0); outvec[i] = (1+pt); mapput(om,invec[i],(1+pt))); outvec; };
xref: Cf. A000010, A081373, A081375 (positions of ones), A210719 (positions of records), A286610.
